
		--------------------Essential git commands -----------------------------

git clone <repo ssh url or https>


	run below 4 commands in sequence for successful file push :
	
			git status : checks status of directory

			git add <file name> : add file to the commit

			git commit -m "commit message"

			git push origin master : pushes changes to git repo
			

git diff <file name> : shows recent change which are not commited

pwd : presen working directory

mkdir : make directory

git commit -m "commit message"

git branch -M main : creates branch with name "main"

git push -u origin main : pushes commited changes to main branch

git rm <file-name> : deletes file

git rm <folder-name> -r : deletes folder

git ls-files : shows files in repo
